Richard D. Isserman



Mr. Richard D. Isserman, CPA, is Independent Director at Movado Group, Inc. and a Member at The American Institute of Certified Public Accountants. He is on the Board of Directors at Movado Group, Inc.
Mr. Isserman was previously employed as Audit Partner by KPMG LLP and a Member by The Jewish Museum.



