Richard D. Isserman, CPA

Age : 81Public asset : 208,666 USDLinked companies :  Movado Group, Inc 





Summary 



Mr. Richard D. Isserman, CPA, is a Member at The American Institute of Certified Public Accountants.He is on the Board of Directors at Movado Group, Inc. Mr. Isserman was previously employed as Audit Partner by KPMG LLP and a Member by The Jewish Museum.



